cards.name: Droplets, Count, Grouped by Build Pack Receipt Build Pack

native.query:
SELECT count(*) AS "count", "public"."droplets"."buildpack_receipt_buildpack" AS "buildpack_receipt_buildpack"
FROM "public"."droplets"
GROUP BY "public"."droplets"."buildpack_receipt_buildpack"
ORDER BY "public"."droplets"."buildpack_receipt_buildpack" ASC

SELECT "public"."events"."id" AS "id", "public"."events"."actee" AS "actee", "public"."events"."actee_name" AS "actee_name", "public"."events"."actee_type" AS "actee_type", "public"."events"."actor" AS "actor", "public"."events"."actor_name" AS "actor_name", "public"."events"."actor_type" AS "actor_type", "public"."events"."actor_username" AS "actor_username", "public"."events"."created_at" AS "created_at", "public"."events"."guid" AS "guid", "public"."events"."metadata" AS "metadata", "public"."events"."organization_guid" AS "organization_guid", "public"."events"."space_guid" AS "space_guid", "public"."events"."timestamp" AS "timestamp", "public"."events"."type" AS "type", "public"."events"."updated_at" AS "updated_at"
FROM "public"."events"
LIMIT 2000

SELECT count(*) AS "count", "public"."apps"."desired_state" AS "desired_state"
FROM "public"."apps"
GROUP BY "public"."apps"."desired_state"
ORDER BY "public"."apps"."desired_state" ASC

cards.name: Count App Usage Events per day

native.query:
SELECT count(*) AS "count", CAST("public"."app_usage_events"."created_at" AS date) AS "created_at"
FROM "public"."app_usage_events"
GROUP BY CAST("public"."app_usage_events"."created_at" AS date)
ORDER BY CAST("public"."app_usage_events"."created_at" AS date) ASC

SELECT app_usage.state, count(*) AS "count"
FROM (SELECT DISTINCT ON ("public"."app_usage_events"."app_guid")
       "public"."app_usage_events"."app_guid" , "public"."app_usage_events"."app_name", CAST("public"."app_usage_events"."created_at" AS date), "public"."app_usage_events"."state" 
FROM "public"."app_usage_events"
WHERE ("public"."app_usage_events".state = 'STOPPED' OR "public"."app_usage_events".state = 'STARTED')
ORDER BY "public"."app_usage_events"."app_guid", CAST("public"."app_usage_events"."created_at" AS date) DESC) AS app_usage
GROUP BY app_usage.state

cards.name: count App Usage Events per app

native.query:
SELECT count(*) AS "count", "public"."app_usage_events"."app_guid" AS "app_guid", "public"."app_usage_events"."app_name" AS "app_name"
FROM "public"."app_usage_events"
GROUP BY "public"."app_usage_events"."app_guid", "public"."app_usage_events"."app_name"
ORDER BY "public"."app_usage_events"."app_guid" ASC, "public"."app_usage_events"."app_name" ASC

SELECT count(*) AS "count" 
FROM "public"."apps"

SELECT count(*) AS "count", "public"."apps"."space_guid" AS "space_guid"
FROM "public"."apps"
GROUP BY "public"."apps"."space_guid"
ORDER BY "public"."apps"."space_guid" ASC

cards.name: count all service bindings per service

native.query:
SELECT "public"."services"."label", count(*) AS "count"
FROM "public"."service_bindings", "public"."service_instances", "public"."service_plans", "public"."services"
WHERE "public"."service_bindings"."service_instance_guid" = "public"."service_instances"."guid"
AND "public"."service_instances"."service_plan_id" = "public"."service_plans"."id"
AND "public"."service_plans"."service_id" = "public"."services"."id"
GROUP BY "public"."services"."id"
ORDER BY "public"."services"."id" ASC

SELECT "public"."service_brokers"."name" AS "service broker","public"."services"."label" AS "service label", "public"."service_plans"."name" AS "service plan",  count(*) AS "service_bindings_count"
FROM "public"."service_bindings", "public"."service_instances", "public"."service_plans", "public"."services", "public"."service_brokers"
WHERE "public"."service_bindings"."service_instance_guid" = "public"."service_instances"."guid"
AND "public"."service_instances"."service_plan_id" = "public"."service_plans"."id"
AND "public"."service_plans"."service_id" = "public"."services"."id"
AND "public"."services"."service_broker_id" = "public"."service_brokers"."id"
GROUP BY "public"."service_brokers"."id", "public"."services"."id", "public"."service_plans"."id"
ORDER BY "public"."service_brokers"."name", "public"."services"."label", "public"."service_plans"."name" ASC

SELECT "public"."service_brokers"."name" AS "service broker","public"."services"."label" AS "service label", "public"."service_plans"."name" AS "service plan",  "public"."organizations"."name" AS "org", "public"."spaces"."name" AS "space", count(*) AS "service_bindings_count"
FROM "public"."service_bindings", "public"."service_instances", "public"."service_plans", "public"."services", "public"."service_brokers", "public"."apps", "public"."organizations", "public"."spaces"
WHERE "public"."service_bindings"."service_instance_guid" = "public"."service_instances"."guid"
AND "public"."service_instances"."service_plan_id" = "public"."service_plans"."id"
AND "public"."service_plans"."service_id" = "public"."services"."id"
AND "public"."services"."service_broker_id" = "public"."service_brokers"."id"
AND "public"."service_bindings"."app_guid" = "public"."apps"."guid"
AND "public"."apps"."space_guid" = "public"."spaces"."guid"
AND "public"."spaces"."organization_id" = "public"."organizations"."id"
GROUP BY "public"."service_brokers"."id", "public"."services"."id", "public"."service_plans"."id", "public"."organizations"."id", "public"."spaces"."id"
ORDER BY "public"."service_brokers"."name", "public"."services"."label", "public"."service_plans"."name", "public"."organizations"."name", "public"."spaces"."name" ASC

cards.name: Top 5 service plan usage in the platform

native.query:

FROM "public"."service_bindings", "public"."service_instances", "public"."service_plans", "public"."services", "public"."service_brokers"

SELECT "public"."users"."id" AS "id", "public"."users"."active" AS "active", "public"."users"."authorities" AS "authorities", "public"."users"."created" AS "created", "public"."users"."email" AS "email", "public"."users"."external_id" AS "external_id", "public"."users"."familyname" AS "familyname", "public"."users"."givenname" AS "givenname", "public"."users"."identity_zone_id" AS "identity_zone_id", "public"."users"."last_logon_success_time" AS "last_logon_success_time", "public"."users"."lastmodified" AS "lastmodified", "public"."users"."legacy_verification_behavior" AS "legacy_verification_behavior", "public"."users"."origin" AS "origin", "public"."users"."passwd_change_required" AS "passwd_change_required", "public"."users"."passwd_lastmodified" AS "passwd_lastmodified", "public"."users"."password" AS "password", "public"."users"."phonenumber" AS "phonenumber", "public"."users"."previous_logon_success_time" AS "previous_logon_success_time", "public"."users"."salt" AS "salt", "public"."users"."username" AS "username", "public"."users"."verified" AS "verified", "public"."users"."version" AS "version"
FROM "public"."users"
LIMIT 2000

SELECT "public"."users"."givenname" AS "givenname", "public"."users"."familyname" AS "familyname", "public"."users"."email" AS "email", "public"."users"."username" AS "username", "public"."users"."created" AS "created"

FROM "public"."users"
WHERE (date_trunc('week', ("public"."users"."created" + INTERVAL '1 day')) - INTERVAL '1 day') = (date_trunc('week', ((NOW() + INTERVAL '-1 week') + INTERVAL '1 day')) - INTERVAL '1 day')
LIMIT 2000

SELECT count(*) AS "count"
FROM "public"."users"
WHERE CAST("public"."users"."created" AS date) BETWEEN CAST((NOW() + INTERVAL '-30 day') AS date)
   AND CAST((NOW() + INTERVAL '-1 day') AS date)

SELECT  "public"."service_brokers"."name" AS "name", 
"public"."service_brokers"."space_id" AS "space_id",
"public"."service_brokers"."created_at" AS "created_at", 
"public"."service_brokers"."broker_url" AS "broker_url"
FROM "public"."service_brokers"
WHERE CAST("public"."service_brokers"."created_at" AS date) BETWEEN CAST((NOW() + INTERVAL '-30 day') AS date)
   AND CAST((NOW() + INTERVAL '-1 day') AS date)
LIMIT 2000

SELECT count(*) AS "count" 
FROM "public"."service_brokers" 
WHERE CAST("public"."service_brokers"."created_at" AS date) BETWEEN CAST((NOW() + INTERVAL '-30 day') AS date)
   AND CAST((NOW() + INTERVAL '-1 day') AS date)

SELECT "public"."users"."username" AS "username", 
"public"."users"."givenname" AS "givenname", 
"public"."users"."familyname" AS "familyname", 
"public"."users"."email" AS "email", 
"public"."users"."created" AS "created"
FROM "public"."users"
WHERE CAST("public"."users"."created" AS date) BETWEEN CAST((NOW() + INTERVAL '-30 day') AS date)
   AND CAST((NOW() + INTERVAL '-1 day') AS date)
LIMIT 2000

SELECT count("public"."apps"."id"), 
"public"."droplets"."buildpack_receipt_buildpack" AS "buildpack_receipt_buildpack"
FROM "public"."apps", "public"."droplets"
WHERE "public"."apps"."droplet_guid" = "public"."droplets"."guid"
GROUP BY "public"."droplets"."buildpack_receipt_buildpack"
ORDER BY count("public"."apps"."id") DESC 
LIMIT 2000

SELECT "public"."service_instances"."updated_at" AS "updated_at", "public"."service_instances"."tags" AS "tags", "public"."service_instances"."syslog_drain_url" AS "syslog_drain_url", "public"."service_instances"."space_id" AS "space_id", "public"."service_instances"."service_plan_id" AS "service_plan_id", "public"."service_instances"."salt" AS "salt", "public"."service_instances"."route_service_url" AS "route_service_url", "public"."service_instances"."name" AS "name", "public"."service_instances"."is_gateway_service" AS "is_gateway_service", "public"."service_instances"."id" AS "id", "public"."service_instances"."guid" AS "guid", "public"."service_instances"."gateway_name" AS "gateway_name", "public"."service_instances"."gateway_data" AS "gateway_data", "public"."service_instances"."dashboard_url" AS "dashboard_url", "public"."service_instances"."credentials" AS "credentials", "public"."service_instances"."created_at" AS "created_at"
FROM "public"."service_instances"
LEFT JOIN "public"."spaces" "spaces__via__space_id" ON "public"."service_instances"."space_id" = "spaces__via__space_id"."id"
WHERE "spaces__via__space_id"."organization_id" = 40
LIMIT 2000

SELECT "public"."service_brokers"."name" AS "service broker","public"."services"."label" AS "service label", "public"."service_plans"."name" AS "service plan",  "public"."organizations"."name" AS "org", count(*) AS "service_bindings_count"
FROM "public"."service_bindings", "public"."service_instances", "public"."service_plans", "public"."services", "public"."service_brokers", "public"."apps", "public"."organizations", "public"."spaces"
WHERE "public"."service_bindings"."service_instance_guid" = "public"."service_instances"."guid"
AND "public"."service_instances"."service_plan_id" = "public"."service_plans"."id"
AND "public"."service_plans"."service_id" = "public"."services"."id"
AND "public"."services"."service_broker_id" = "public"."service_brokers"."id"
AND "public"."service_bindings"."app_guid" = "public"."apps"."guid"
AND "public"."apps"."space_guid" = "public"."spaces"."guid"
AND "public"."spaces"."organization_id" = "public"."organizations"."id"
[[AND "public"."organizations"."name" = {{organization}}]]
GROUP BY "public"."service_brokers"."id", "public"."services"."id", "public"."service_plans"."id", "public"."organizations"."id"
ORDER BY "public"."service_brokers"."name", "public"."services"."label", "public"."service_plans"."name", "public"."organizations"."name" ASC

SELECT
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name" AS "Organization",
  "spaces__via__space_id"."name" AS "Space",
  "services__via__service_id"."label" AS "Service",
  "service_plans__via__service_pl"."name" AS "Service plan",
  count(*) AS "Number of instances"
FROM "public"."service_instances"
LEFT JOIN "public"."service_plans" "service_plans__via__service_pl" ON "public"."service_instances"."service_plan_id" = "service_plans__via__service_pl"."id"
LEFT JOIN "public"."services" "services__via__service_id" ON "service_plans__via__service_pl"."service_id" = "services__via__service_id"."id"
LEFT JOIN "public"."spaces" "spaces__via__space_id" ON "public"."service_instances"."space_id" = "spaces__via__space_id"."id"
LEFT JOIN "public"."organizations" "organizations__via__organization_id" ON "spaces__via__space_id"."organization_id" = "organizations__via__organization_id"."id"
GROUP BY
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name",
  "spaces__via__space_id"."name",
  "service_plans__via__service_pl"."name",
  "services__via__service_id"."label"
ORDER BY
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name" ASC,
  "spaces__via__space_id"."name" ASC,
  "service_plans__via__service_pl"."name" ASC
LIMIT 20000;

SELECT
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name" AS "Organization",
  "services__via__service_id"."label" AS "Service",
  "service_plans__via__service_pl"."name" AS "Service plan",
  count(*) AS "Number of instances"
FROM "public"."service_instances"
LEFT JOIN "public"."service_plans" "service_plans__via__service_pl" ON "public"."service_instances"."service_plan_id" = "service_plans__via__service_pl"."id"
LEFT JOIN "public"."services" "services__via__service_id" ON "service_plans__via__service_pl"."service_id" = "services__via__service_id"."id"
LEFT JOIN "public"."spaces" "spaces__via__space_id" ON "public"."service_instances"."space_id" = "spaces__via__space_id"."id"
LEFT JOIN "public"."organizations" "organizations__via__organization_id" ON "spaces__via__space_id"."organization_id" = "organizations__via__organization_id"."id"
GROUP BY
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name",
  "service_plans__via__service_pl"."name",
  "services__via__service_id"."label"
ORDER BY
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name" ASC,
  "service_plans__via__service_pl"."name" ASC
LIMIT 20000;

cards.description: Return RAM used for desired "STARTED" apps.
cards.name: RAM used by Organizations

native.query:
SELECT
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name" AS "Organization",
  sum("memory" * "instances") AS "Memory used (MB)"
FROM "public"."processes"
LEFT JOIN "public"."apps"          "apps__via__app_guid"                 ON "public"."processes"."app_guid"           = "apps__via__app_guid"."guid"
LEFT JOIN "public"."spaces"        "spaces__via__space_guid"             ON "apps__via__app_guid"."space_guid"        = "spaces__via__space_guid"."guid"
LEFT JOIN "public"."organizations" "organizations__via__organization_id" ON "spaces__via__space_guid"."organization_id" = "organizations__via__organization_id"."id"
WHERE
  "apps__via__app_guid"."desired_state" = 'STARTED'
GROUP BY
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name"
ORDER BY
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name" ASC
LIMIT 20000;

cards.description: Return RAM used for desired "STARTED" apps.
cards.name: RAM used by Spaces

native.query:
SELECT
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name" AS "Organization",
  "spaces__via__space_guid"."name" AS "Space",
  sum("memory" * "instances") AS "Memory used (MB)"
FROM "public"."processes"
LEFT JOIN "public"."apps"          "apps__via__app_guid"                 ON "public"."processes"."app_guid"           = "apps__via__app_guid"."guid"
LEFT JOIN "public"."spaces"        "spaces__via__space_guid"             ON "apps__via__app_guid"."space_guid"        = "spaces__via__space_guid"."guid"
LEFT JOIN "public"."organizations" "organizations__via__organization_id" ON "spaces__via__space_guid"."organization_id" = "organizations__via__organization_id"."id"
WHERE
  "apps__via__app_guid"."desired_state" = 'STARTED'
GROUP BY
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name",
  "spaces__via__space_guid"."name"
ORDER BY
  "organizations__via__organization_id"."name" ASC,
  "spaces__via__space_guid"."name" ASC
LIMIT 20000;

cards.description: Applications using mySQL, sorted by application usage events count
cards.name: Applications using mySQL

native.query:
SELECT "public"."app_usage_events"."app_guid" AS "app_guid", "public"."apps"."name" AS "name" , "public"."organizations"."name" AS "org", "public"."spaces"."name" AS "space", count(*) AS "usage_count"  
FROM "public"."service_bindings", "public"."service_instances", "public"."service_plans", "public"."services", "public"."service_brokers", "public"."apps", "public"."app_usage_events",  "public"."organizations", "public"."spaces"
WHERE "public"."service_bindings"."service_instance_guid" = "public"."service_instances"."guid"
AND "public"."service_instances"."service_plan_id" = "public"."service_plans"."id"
AND "public"."service_plans"."service_id" = "public"."services"."id"
AND "public"."services"."service_broker_id" = "public"."service_brokers"."id"
AND "public"."service_bindings"."app_guid" = "public"."apps"."guid"
AND "public"."app_usage_events"."app_guid" = "public"."apps"."guid"
AND "public"."apps"."space_guid" = "public"."spaces"."guid"
AND "public"."spaces"."organization_id" = "public"."organizations"."id"
AND "public"."service_brokers"."name"='p-mysql'
AND "public"."apps"."desired_state" = 'STARTED'
GROUP BY "public"."app_usage_events"."app_guid", "public"."apps"."name", "public"."organizations"."name" , "public"."spaces"."name"
ORDER BY "usage_count" DESC, "name" ASC
